u003cdiv style=\"font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#f87171; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.5px; margin-bottom:10px;\"\u003eTrump \u0026amp; Iran Narrative Watch\u003c/div\u003e\u003cul style=\"margin:0; padding-left:18px; font-size:13px;\"\u003e\u003cli style=\"margin-bottom:8px; color:#94a3b8; line-height:1.6;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDraft Narrative:\u003c/strong\u003e The Drive briefing frames weekend diplomacy as a major de-escalation and Strait of Hormuz reopening story. Treat the fine detail as narrative unless confirmed by live official statements or reliable news flow.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli style=\"margin-bottom:8px; color:#94a3b8; line-height:1.6;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEnergy Transmission:\u003c/strong\u003e The market impact remains straightforward: lower war-risk premium in crude drains inflation pressure; any reversal would hit yields and index liquidity quickly.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv style=\"background:rgba(251,191,36,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(251,191,36,0.25); border-radius:8px; padding:14px 16px; margin-bottom:12px;\"\u003e\u003cdiv style=\"font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#fbbf24; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.5px; margin-bottom:10px;\"\u003eFed Chair Kevin Warsh Watch\u003c/div\u003e\u003cul style=\"margin:0; padding-left:18px; font-size:13px;\"\u003e\u003cli style=\"margin-bottom:8px; color:#94a3b8; line-height:1.6;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Gavel Awaits:\u003c/strong\u003e The draft frames the June 16 meeting as the first Warsh-led FOMC session. The verified calendar confirms the June 16-17 meeting window.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli style=\"margin-bottom:8px; color:#94a3b8; line-height:1.6;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStrategic Ambiguity:\u003c/strong\u003e The key trade is whether compressed rates volatility survives the meeting communication. Watch dots, statement tone, and press-conference signaling rather than unofficial chatter.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div